    "Unfortunately, this state information cannot be simply left out of the checkpoint as it is essential for a successful restart of the training process.",
    "Coupled with the already large number of LLM parameters (billions), the overall checkpoint size becomes massive.",
    "Even worse, while the size of checkpoints grows proportionally to the number of transformer layers, it grows quadratically with respect to the number of hidden dimensions [33].",
